01:02:20,808 --> 01:02:22,009
Why is he here?

1035
01:02:22,042 --> 01:02:23,377
I think it's because of
grandma.

1036
01:02:23,410 --> 01:02:24,979
No, no, you said they weren't
a thing.

1037
01:02:25,012 --> 01:02:27,181
- They're not.
