There's something else.

1041
01:02:34,388 --> 01:02:36,090
What, what else?

1042
01:02:36,123 --> 01:02:37,491
Josh, I need to tell you
something.

1043
01:02:37,525 --> 01:02:40,127
What, what, Charlotte, what?

1044
01:02:41,462 --> 01:02:43,964
There you are, missy.

1045
01:02:43,998 --> 01:02:48,202
