01:04:21,195 --> 01:04:23,263
[yawns] Amy is sound asleep.

1086
01:04:23,297 --> 01:04:25,899
I don't think she missed us one
bit.

1087
01:04:25,933 --> 01:04:28,135
Gosh, seeing those kids tonight

1088
01:04:28,168 --> 01:04:30,137
