Come on, why did you stop
playing?

1095
01:04:44,485 --> 01:04:46,153
Because I quit auditioning.

1096
01:04:46,186 --> 01:04:47,054
Why?

1097
01:04:48,021 --> 01:04:50,991
'Cause that curmudgeon
conductor said my bow work

1098
