1119
01:06:04,064 --> 01:06:06,768
Mm.
[Milo laughs]

1120
01:06:06,801 --> 01:06:10,337
♪ But then you croon a note or
two ♪

1121
01:06:10,370 --> 01:06:14,041
♪ And soon my will to fight is
through ♪

1122
01:06:14,074 --> 01:06:19,079
♪ You sing my doubts and fears
