01:06:38,265 --> 01:06:41,603
♪ That washes me along ♪

1129
01:06:41,636 --> 01:06:46,641
♪ I'm a prisoner of your siren
song ♪

1130
01:06:51,345 --> 01:06:56,183
♪ Yes your siren song ♪

1131
01:06:56,216 --> 01:06:58,352
[fire crackling]

1132
01:06:58,385 --> 01:07:01,054
[Josh sighing]

